<subSubSection pageId="35" pageNumber="36" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph blockId="35.[151,1436,1016,1295]" box="[151,557,1016,1043]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,530,1016,1043]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Number of specimens recorded.</emphasis>
2.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="35.[151,1436,1016,1295]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,1052,1079]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Distribution.</emphasis>
Western, southern and southeastern Europe. 
<collectingCountry box="[861,960,1053,1079]" name="Portugal" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Portugal</collectingCountry>
: one province (Estremadura) in this study, and Algarve (Dyte unpubl. data).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="35.[151,1436,1016,1295]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,300,1125,1151]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Ecology.</emphasis>
The only Portuguese sampling site with this species was a coastal lagoon with saltmarshes surrounded mostly by pine forest and plantations of 
<taxonomicName box="[603,766,1161,1187]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Eucalyptus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis box="[603,727,1161,1187]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Eucalyptus</emphasis>
sp.
</taxonomicName>
In northwestern Europe, this species is also confined to salt marshes and brackish marshes (
<bibRefCitation author="Pollet, M." box="[505,641,1197,1223]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" pagination="1 - 190" refId="ref34362" refString="Pollet, M. (2000) A documented Red List of the dolichopodid flies (Diptera: Dolichopodidae) of Flanders [in Dutch with English summary]. Communications of the Institute of Nature Conservation, 8, 1 - 190." type="journal article" year="2000">Pollet 2000</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="35.[151,1436,1016,1295]" box="[199,638,1232,1259]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,337,1232,1259]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Rarity (%).</emphasis>
1.1 (very rare). Rare (FL).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="35.[151,1436,1016,1295]" box="[199,519,1268,1295]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,386,1268,1295]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Activity period.</emphasis>
